@node Introduction "Introduction to iffDT"

  @{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

 @{b}iffDT@{ub} is a @{"DataTypes" link DataTypes} subclass for loading and displaying iff-files. Once installed it will let all @{"DataTypes" link DataTypes} aware programs to recognize and load iff-files and view its contents as text.
@endnode

@node Requirements "Requirements for iffDT"

  @{b}@{u}Requirements@{uu}@{ub}

 @{b}iffDT@{ub} requires AmigaDOS 3.0 or higher (@{i}datatypes.library @{ui}).
 @{b}iffDT@{ub} requires also the hypertext.datatype ® by Stefan Ruppert.
@endnode

@node Installation "Installation of iffDT"

  @{b}@{u}Installation@{uu}@{ub}

 Use supplied @{i}Installer @{ui}script to copy necessary files. If you go for "Manually Selectable" installation you will need to activate class by double-clicking on @{i}DEVS:DataTypes/iff @{ui} icon or using @{i}AddDataTypes @{b}REFRESH @{ub}@{ui}from Shell.
@endnode

@node Configuration "Configuring operation of iffDT"

  @{b}@{u}Configuration@{uu}@{ub}

 Please use for configurating the Datatype @{b}DTpref@{ub}.


